  <h1>
   File System
  </h1>
  There exists in
  <span>
   GameMaker
  </span>
  a number of functions that enable you to manipulate files of all types in different ways:
  <ul>
   <li>
    <a href="file_exists.htm">
     file_exists
    </a>
   </li>
   <li>
    <a href="file_delete.htm">
     file_delete
    </a>
   </li>
   <li>
    <a href="file_rename.htm">
     file_rename
    </a>
   </li>
   <li>
    <a href="file_copy.htm">
     file_copy
    </a>
   </li>
   <li>
    <a href="file_find_first.htm">
